        <mxCell id="leg9" value="Services removed vs SRS v1.0:&#xa;✗ Amazon Athena (no functional req)&#xa;✗ AWS Glue (replaced by bulk-ingestion Lambda)&#xa;✗ ElastiCache Redis (replaced by pg materialized views)&#xa;✗ RDS Proxy (200 user cap managed by Lambda concurrency)&#xa;✗ CloudFront standalone (built into Amplify)" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=#fee2e2;strokeColor=#ef4444;align=left;fontSize=9;fontColor=#0F172A;rounded=1;" vertex="1" parent="legend">
